Company Overview of Evercore Trust Company, N.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Evercore Trust Company, N.A., a national trust bank, provides investment management, independent fiduciary, and trustee services for employee benefit plans. The company offers investments in employer stock services, such as defined benefit and contribution plans, and proxy voting; independent fiduciary services, including settlement, prohibited transaction exemption, institutional trust, and trustee services; and personal trust services, which include wealth transfer planning, investment management, family governance, exercise of discretion, and estate settlement, as well as custody, safekeeping, and recordkeeping services. It also act as executor, personal representative, sole trustee, co-t...
Evercore Trust Company, N.A., a national trust bank, provides investment management, independent fiduciary, and trustee services for employee benefit plans. The company offers investments in employer stock services, such as defined benefit and contribution plans, and proxy voting; independent fiduciary services, including settlement, prohibited transaction exemption, institutional trust, and trustee services; and personal trust services, which include wealth transfer planning, investment management, family governance, exercise of discretion, and estate settlement, as well as custody, safekeeping, and recordkeeping services. It also act as executor, personal representative, sole trustee, co-trustee, and successor trustee taking legal responsibility for carrying out the terms of the instrument for estates and includable, revocable, charitable, generation-skipping, and special needs/special purpose trusts. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in New York, New York. Evercore Trust Company, N.A. operates as a subsidiary of Evercore L.P.
Detailed Description


